These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
Cigar: bolivar, montecristo
Flower: amaryllis, marigold
1. Cigar:bolivar is on the left of Flower:amaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Cigar   | bolivar  | montecristo |
| Flower     | marigold | amaryllis  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
Game: whist, chess
Cigar: old-henry, davidoff
1. Game:chess is on the right of Cigar:old-henry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Game    | whist      | chess         |
| Cigar   | old-henry | davidoff |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
City: edinburgh, miami
Transport: scooter, taxi
1. City:edinburgh is on the right of Transport:taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| City   | miami | edinburgh   |
| Transport       | taxi  | scooter |

 #################################
 
